<div class="cs-content">
  <div class="cs-content__inner">
    <h1>Prospective Undergraduate Students</h1>
  </div>
  <div class="cs-content__inner">

    {# ── WELCOME ── #}
    <section class="cs-ug-intro">
      <div class="cs-ug-intro__text">
        <h2 class="cs-section-label">Your Journey Starts Here</h2>
        <p>
          Interested in studying Computer Science at Stellenbosch University? You're in the right place.
          This page covers everything you need to know about admission requirements, how to apply, and
          what to expect when you arrive on campus.
        </p>
      </div>
    </section>

    {# ── ADMISSION REQUIREMENTS ── #}
    <section class="cs-ug-admission">
      <h2 class="cs-section-label cs-section-label--center">Admission Requirements</h2>
      <div class="cs-ug-req-grid">
        <div class="cs-ug-req-card">
          <div class="cs-ug-req-card__icon">
            <svg width="28" height="28" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5"><path d="M22 10v6M2 10l10-5 10 5-10 5z"/><path d="M6 12v5c3 3 9 3 12 0v-5"/></svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="cs-ug-req-card__title">NSC or Equivalent</h3>
          <p>A National Senior Certificate (or equivalent qualification such as IEB) that meets the minimum faculty requirements for admission to the BSc programme.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="cs-ug-req-card">
          <div class="cs-ug-req-card__icon">
            <svg width="28" height="28" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5"><path d="M4 19.5A2.5 2.5 0 0 1 6.5 17H20"/><path d="M6.5 2H20v20H6.5A2.5 2.5 0 0 1 4 19.5v-15A2.5 2.5 0 0 1 6.5 2z"/></svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="cs-ug-req-card__title">Mathematics 70%+</h3>
          <p>A strong mathematics grade is essential. We recommend a minimum of 70% in NSC Mathematics for competitive admission.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="cs-ug-req-card">
          <div class="cs-ug-req-card__icon">
            <svg width="28" height="28" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5"><path d="M14.7 6.3a1 1 0 0 0 0 1.4l1.6 1.6a1 1 0 0 0 1.4 0l3.77-3.77a6 6 0 0 1-7.94 7.94l-6.91 6.91a2.12 2.12 0 0 1-3-3l6.91-6.91a6 6 0 0 1 7.94-7.94l-3.76 3.76z"/></svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="cs-ug-req-card__title">Physical Sciences</h3>
          <p>A good grade in Physical Sciences is beneficial and may be required for certain streams such as Computer Systems.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="cs-ug-req-card">
          <div class="cs-ug-req-card__icon">
            <svg width="28" height="28" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5"><path d="M12 22s8-4 8-10V5l-8-3-8 3v7c0 6 8 10 8 10z"/></svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="cs-ug-req-card__title">Language Requirements</h3>
          <p>Proficiency in English is required. Instruction is available in both English and Afrikaans for most first-year modules.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    {# ── HOW TO APPLY ── #}
    <section class="cs-ug-apply">
      <h2 class="cs-section-label cs-section-label--center">How to Apply</h2>
      <div class="cs-ug-steps">
        <div class="cs-ug-step">
          <span class="cs-ug-step__number">1</span>
          <div class="cs-ug-step__content">
            <h3>Visit Stellenbosch University Admissions</h3>
            <p>Go to <a href="https://www.sun.ac.za" target="_blank">www.sun.ac.za</a> and navigate to the online admissions portal.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="cs-ug-step">
          <span class="cs-ug-step__number">2</span>
          <div class="cs-ug-step__content">
            <h3>Submit Your Application</h3>
            <p>Complete the online form with your academic records, personal details, and documentation. Choose BSc Computer Science or BDatSci as your programme.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="cs-ug-step">
          <span class="cs-ug-step__number">3</span>
          <div class="cs-ug-step__content">
            <h3>Meet the Deadline</h3>
            <p>Applications typically close in <strong>September</strong> of the year before enrolment. Check the university website for exact dates each year.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="cs-ug-step">
          <span class="cs-ug-step__number">4</span>
          <div class="cs-ug-step__content">
            <h3>Receive Your Offer</h3>
            <p>Once accepted, you'll receive a formal offer. Contact our department directly for any CS-specific questions about your programme.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    {# ── AVAILABLE PROGRAMMES ── #}
    <section class="cs-ug-avail">
      <h2 class="cs-section-label cs-section-label--center">Available Programmes</h2>
      <div class="cs-ug-avail__grid">
        <a href="/undergraduate/programmes" class="cs-ug-avail-card">
          <span class="cs-ug-avail-card__type">BSc</span>
          <span class="cs-ug-avail-card__name">Computer Science</span>
          <span class="cs-ug-avail-card__detail">5 focal areas · 3 years</span>
        </a>
        <a href="/undergraduate/programmes" class="cs-ug-avail-card">
          <span class="cs-ug-avail-card__type">BDatSci</span>
          <span class="cs-ug-avail-card__name">Data Science</span>
          <span class="cs-ug-avail-card__detail">Interdisciplinary · 4 years</span>
        </a>
      </div>
    </section>

    {# ── STUDENT SUPPORT ── #}
    <section class="cs-ug-support">
      <h2 class="cs-section-label cs-section-label--center">Student Support</h2>
      <p class="cs-ug-support__lead">We're committed to helping every student succeed.</p>
      <div class="cs-ug-support__grid">
        <div class="cs-ug-support-item">
          <svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5"><path d="M17 21v-2a4 4 0 0 0-4-4H5a4 4 0 0 0-4 4v2"/><circle cx="9" cy="7" r="4"/><path d="M23 21v-2a4 4 0 0 0-3-3.87"/><path d="M16 3.13a4 4 0 0 1 0 7.75"/></svg>
          <h3>Tutoring &amp; Mentoring</h3>
          <p>Dedicated tutors and peer mentors support you through every module.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="cs-ug-support-item">
          <svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5"><rect x="2" y="3" width="20" height="14" rx="2"/><path d="M8 21h8M12 17v4"/></svg>
          <h3>Modern Facilities</h3>
          <p>Access to well-equipped computer labs, study spaces, and software resources.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="cs-ug-support-item">
          <svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5"><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"/><path d="M16 8l-4 4-4-4"/></svg>
          <h3>Career Guidance</h3>
          <p>Internship placements, career advising, and connections to top employers.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="cs-ug-support-item">
          <svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5"><path d="M21 15a2 2 0 0 1-2 2H7l-4 4V5a2 2 0 0 1 2-2h14a2 2 0 0 1 2 2z"/></svg>
          <h3>Study Groups</h3>
          <p>Peer learning sessions, group projects, and a supportive student community.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    {# ── CTA ── #}
    <section class="cs-about-cta">
      <h2 class="cs-about-cta__heading">Questions? We're Here to Help</h2>
      <p class="cs-about-cta__text">Get in touch with our undergraduate admissions office or explore our programmes.</p>
      <div class="cs-about-cta__buttons">
        <a href="/contact" class="cs-about-cta__btn cs-about-cta__btn--primary">Contact Us</a>
        <a href="/undergraduate" class="cs-about-cta__btn cs-about-cta__btn--secondary">Undergraduate Overview →</a>
      </div>
    </section>

  </div>
</div>
